<i>adjective</i>: 냉철하다 [냉ː철하다] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt>냉철하다 [냉ː철하다]</dt><br>
<dd>level-headed; self-possessed</dd><br>
<dd>생각이나 판단이 감정에 치우치지 않고 침착하며 정확하다.</dd><br>
<dd>One's thinking or judgment being exact, composed, and not swayed by one's emotions.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>